OptimumBank Holdings, Inc. Key Developments

OptimumBank Holdings, Inc., Annual General Meeting, Apr 25, 2017
Mar 24 17
OptimumBank Holdings, Inc., Annual General Meeting, Apr 25, 2017, at 10:00 US Eastern Standard Time. Location: OptimumBank, 2477 East Commercial Boulevard Fort Lauderdale, FL 33308 United States Agenda: To elect four directors; to ratify the selection of Hacker, Johnson & Smith PA as the company’s independent auditor for fiscal year 2017; to consider an advisory vote on executive compensation; and to transact such other business as may properly come before the annual meeting.


OptimumBank Holdings, Inc. Auditor Raises 'Going Concern' Doubt
Mar 20 17
OptimumBank Holdings, Inc. filed its 10-K on Mar 20, 2017 for the period ending Dec 31, 2016. In this report its auditor, Hacker, Johnson & Smith PA, gave an unqualified opinion expressing doubt that the company can continue as a going concern.


John H. Clifford Joins Board of Directors of OptimumBank Holdings, Inc. and OptimumBank
Oct 31 16
OptimumBank Holdings Inc. announced that John H. Clifford has joined the Board of Directors of OptimumBank Holdings (company) and OptimumBank (Bank). Also, the company announced that Norman Ginsparg has resigned from the Board of Directors of the Bank for personal reasons.


