Several equities analysts have commented on the company. Cowen and Company  reiterated a “buy” rating and set a $27.00 price target on shares of Embraer-Empresa Brasileira de Aeronautica in a report on Thursday, April 13th. Zacks Investment Research downgraded Embraer-Empresa Brasileira de Aeronautica from a “hold” rating to a “strong sell” rating in a report on Thursday, May 11th. ValuEngine downgraded shares of Embraer-Empresa Brasileira de Aeronautica from a “buy” rating to a “hold” rating in a research note on Wednesday, June 7th. Finally, TheStreet downgraded shares of Embraer-Empresa Brasileira de Aeronautica from a “b-” rating to a “c+” rating in a research note on Wednesday, April 5th. One investment analyst  has rated the stock with a sell rating, four have issued  a hold rating and four have issued  a buy rating to the company’s stock. The company presently has an average rating of “Hold” and a consensus target price of $22.60.
