Industry: 



OptimumBank was founded November, 2000 by a group of local Broward County businessmen led by Albert Finch and Richard Browdy. They decided to reverse the trend of out of state mega-banks and give the area a true community bank. In the spirit of a "true" community bank, the directors gave local investors, both big and small, a chance to own a piece of the new bank. The bank is initially focusing on traditional in-person banking with business and consumers residing in South Florida. Our customers found a new bank that isn't charging the exorbitant fees they were experiencing at the larger financial institutions, a bank having unmatched expertise in residential and commercial real estate
 Please check Optimumbank Holdings, Inc. for more information.


















