OptimumBank Holdings, Inc. (OPHC) Upgraded at ValuEngine


					Posted by Chloe McGuire on Jul 7th, 2017 // No Comments




OptimumBank Holdings, Inc. (NASDAQ:OPHC) was upgraded by investment analysts at ValuEngine from a “strong sell” rating to a “sell” rating in a research report issued on Friday, June 2nd.
Shares of OptimumBank Holdings (NASDAQ:OPHC) opened at 2.9835 on Friday. The stock’s 50 day moving average is $2.76 and its 200 day moving average is $3.35. OptimumBank Holdings has a 1-year low of $2.11 and a 1-year high of $6.45. The company’s market cap is $3.29 million. 


