			Company Description 


			OptimumBank Holdings, Inc. operates as a bank holding company for OptimumBank. The Bank offers a variety of community banking services to individual and corporate customers. It offers an array of lending and retail banking products to individuals and businesses. The company was founded on March 23, ...
		


                OptimumBank Holdings, Inc. operates as a bank holding company for OptimumBank. The Bank offers a variety of community banking services to individual and corporate customers. It offers an array of lending and retail banking products to individuals and businesses. The company was founded on March 23, 2004 and is headquartered in Fort Lauderdale, FL.
            




