OptimumBank Holdings Inc: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback
















optimumbank holdings inc
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Banking
Sub-Industry: Banks
OptimumBank Holdings Inc provides retail banking, commercial banking, and real estate lending services and products.  The Bank serves individuals and businesses in  Broward, Dade, and Palm Beach counties, all located in Florida. OptimumBank also offers Internet banking services through its Web site.




